OL,3,CMan targeted in race hate attack for
OL,4,Cthird time
OL,6,FA Nigerian man who had his car set on
OL,7,Ffire in Newtownabbey has said he has
OL,8,Fbeen targeted three times in the last
OL,9,Fnumber of months.
OL,11,FThe arson happened outside a house on
OL,12,FMournebeg Drive in the Rathcoole
OL,13,Festate.
OL,15,FElsewhere, two people were injured
OL,16,Fafter being attacked by a group of men
OL,17,Fas they left a house in south Belfast.
OL,19,FPolice are treating both incidents as
OL,20,Fracially-motivated hate crimes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
