PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781606875
OL,3,CMan targeted in race hate attack for
OL,4,Cthird time
OL,6,FThey are the latest in a string of
OL,7,Fattacks in Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,10,Ffollowing the arson attack in
OL,11,FNewtownabbey on Sunday night.
OL,13,FSergeant Knox said: "At approximately
OL,14,F11.40pm, it was reported that a
OL,15,Fvehicle was set alight in the
OL,16,FMournebeg Drive area.
OL,18,F"Officers attended along with
OL,19,Fcolleagues from Northern Ireland Fire
OL,20,FService, who extinguished the fire.
OL,21,FThere were no reports of any injuries.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781606875
OL,3,CMan targeted in race hate attack for
OL,4,Cthird time
OL,6,F"Enquiries are continuing to establish
OL,7,Fthe circumstances of the incident,
OL,8,Fwhich is being treated as a racially
OL,9,Fmotivated hate crime at this time.
OL,11,F"We are keen to hear from anyone who
OL,12,Fnoticed any suspicious behaviour at
OL,13,Fthe time of the report, or had
OL,14,Fwitnessed a male on an e-scooter in
OL,15,Fthe area."
OL,17,FMeanwhile, a woman and children were
OL,18,Finside the house which was targeted in
OL,19,Fthe Donegall Avenue of south Belfast
OL,20,Fon Sunday morning.
