OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781606875
OL,3,CMan targeted in race hate attack for
OL,4,Cthird time
OL,6,FA man has been charged aggravated
OL,7,Fburglary with intent to commit
OL,8,Funlawful damage, criminal damage and
OL,9,Ftwo counts of common assault.
OL,11,FHe was due to appear before Belfast
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Monday.
OL,14,FA 22-year-old who was arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of the same offences has
OL,16,Fbeen released on bail to allow for
OL,17,Ffurther police enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
