OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781606875
OL,3,CMan targeted in race hate attack for
OL,4,Cthird time
OL,6,FThe incidents come after thousands of
OL,7,Fpeople attended an anti-racism rally
OL,8,Fin Belfast on Saturday following days
OL,9,Fof unrest.
OL,11,FDisorder broke out across the city in
OL,12,Fthe wake of a knife attack which saw
OL,13,Fthe victim lose an eye and suffer deep
OL,14,Fcuts to his head, face and back.
